'''克莱顿·安德鲁·唐纳德森'''（{{lang-en|'''Clayton Andrew Donaldson'''}}，{{bd|1984年|2月7日|catIdx=Donaldson, Clayton}}）是一名[[牙買加|牙買加]]籍[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|布拉德福德]]。

==早年==
唐纳德森生於[[西约克郡|西约克郡]][[布拉德福德|布拉德福德]]<ref name="Hugman2010-11"/>，求學時期已在學校踢足球。他自小便是[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|布拉德福德]]球迷，曾加入球會的青年軍，但16歲時未能獲得一紙合約而被釋出，之後他與[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]的青年隊教練發挖而簽約加盟該會青年軍<ref>{{cite news |title=Former Hull City youngster Clayton Donaldson returns as 'strike leader' for Birmingham City |url=http://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/Hull-City-youngster-Clayton-Donaldson-returns/story-28036151-detail/story.html |newspaper=Hull Daily Mail |date=23 October 2015 |accessdate=25 November 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217165114/http://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/hull-city-youngster-clayton-donaldson-returns/story-28036151-detail/story.html |archivedate=2016年12月17日 }}</ref>。

==球會生涯==
===赫尔城===
唐纳德森首場職業比賽是2002年10月22日[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]3-1不敵[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|韦尔港]]的賽事，在60分鐘換入，當時他仍是球隊的青年軍一員<ref name="Hugman2010-11"/><ref name="Port Vale 3–1 Hull">{{Cite news| title = Port Vale 3–1 Hull| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2344805.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 22 October 2002| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423120813/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2344805.stm}}</ref>。2002年11月，他被外借到[[英格蘭北部超級聯賽|英格蘭北部超級聯賽]]球會[[哈羅蓋特鎮足球會|哈羅蓋特鎮]]<ref name="Latest transfers">{{Cite news| title = Latest transfers| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?&newsmode=FULL&nid=7011| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 9 November 2002| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140405003621/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?&newsmode=FULL&nid=7011| archivedate = 2014年4月5日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>，在新球會首秀便取得進球，11月12日作客[[盖茨黑德足球俱乐部|盖茨黑德]]的賽事他在68分鐘打進一球使球隊以3-1取勝<ref name="Victory in our grasp – Reed">{{Cite news| title = Victory in our grasp – Reed| url = http://www.harrogateadvertiser.co.uk/sport/victory-in-our-grasp-reed-1-2721225| newspaper = Harrogate Advertiser| date = 14 November 2002| accessdate = 4 April 2014| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508025127/http://www.harrogateadvertiser.co.uk/sport/victory-in-our-grasp-reed-1-2721225| archive-date = 2016-05-08| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。他在[[英格兰足球联赛|英格兰足球联赛]]首場比賽是2003年2月8日代表赫爾城在81分鐘換入[[達米安·德拉尼|達米安·德拉尼]]，最終以1-0輸給[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]。兩天後，他與球會簽下兩年職業合約<ref name="Hugman2010-11"/><ref name="Clayton Donaldson">{{cite web| title = Clayton Donaldson| url = http://www.oncloudseven.com/donaldson-c.htm| publisher = On Cloud Seven| accessdate = 4 April 2014| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140405004204/http://www.oncloudseven.com/donaldson-c.htm| archivedate = 2014年4月5日}}</ref>。

2003年8月，唐纳德森被外借至[[英格蘭足球議會聯賽|英格蘭足球議會聯賽]]球會[[斯卡布羅足球會|斯卡布羅]]三個月<ref name="Slade brings in Donaldson">{{cite news| title = Slade brings in Donaldson| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=12109| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 23 August 2003| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214192601/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=12109| archivedate = 2012年2月14日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>，首場比賽是2003年8月23日主場以2-1不敵[[保顿艾尔宾足球俱乐部|保顿艾尔宾足球俱乐部]]。此外，外借期間他還有另一次聯賽上場和兩次聯賽錦標上場機會，以4次上場記錄結束他的斯卡布羅之旅<ref name="Non League Club Directory 2005 1">{{cite book |editor1-first=Mike |editor1-last=Williams |editor2-first=Tony |editor2-last=Williams |title=Non League Club Directory 2005 |year=2004 |publisher=Tony Williams Publications |location= |isbn=978-1-869833-49-7 |pages=142–143}}</ref>。2004年2月他被外借到[[哈利法哈斯鎮足球會|哈利法哈斯鎮]]一個月<ref name="Halifax take Donaldson">{{Cite news| title = Halifax take Donaldson| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/3472815.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 9 February 2004| accessdate = 11 July 2011}}</ref>，2月8日首次代表新球會上場，在58入鐘入替，最終以2-0不敵[[馬格特足球會|馬格特]]。這段外借之旅他共有四次上場記錄<ref name="Non League Club Directory 2005 2">{{cite book |editor1-last=Williams |editor2-last=Williams |title=Non League Club Directory 2005 |pages=112–113}}</ref>。2004/05球季，由於唐纳德森在赫爾城的上場機會並不大，於是他在9月被外借回哈羅蓋特鎮一個月，9月18日重回哈羅蓋特鎮首秀便打進一球，以3-0擊敗[[蘭卡斯特足球會|蘭卡斯特]]<ref name="Harrogate snap up Duxbury">{{cite news| title = Harrogate snap up Duxbury| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=20487| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 16 September 2004| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214192638/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=20487| archivedate = 2012年2月14日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>。2004年10月，唐纳德森被選為[[英格蘭足球議會北部聯賽|英格蘭足球議會北部聯賽]]當月最佳球員，該月他在5場比賽中打進3球<ref name="Vieira is Nationwide Conference Player of the Month">{{cite news| title = Vieira is Nationwide Conference Player of the Month| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=21921| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 9 November 2004| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140405004440/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=21921| archivedate = 2014年4月5日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>。唐纳德森在哈羅蓋特鎮的第二次外借之旅以11場4球成績結束，到2004/05球季季末，由於赫爾城教練[[彼得·泰勒|彼得·泰勒]]未能保證他在一隊有上場時間，於是被球會放棄釋出<ref name="Hinds And Donaldson Released">{{cite news| title = Hinds And Donaldson Released| url = http://www.hullcityafc.net/page/NewsDetail/0,,10338~664655,00.html| publisher = Hull City A.F.C| date = 17 May 2005| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120329134646/http://www.hullcityafc.net/page/NewsDetail/0,,10338~664655,00.html| archivedate = 2012年3月29日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>。

===約克城===
被赫爾城釋出後，唐纳德森曾與[[巴罗足球俱乐部|巴罗]]傾談合約事宜<ref name="Turnbull`s targets">{{Cite news| title = Turnbull's targets| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=27803| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 27 June 2005| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120310052347/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=27803| archivedate = 2012年3月10日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>，但他最終在2005年6月與[[約克城足球會|約克城]]簽約。他在約克城首個球季便打進18球，使他當選為球會年度最佳球員<ref name="The Complete Record 2005-06">{{cite book |first=David |last=Batters |title=York City: The Complete Record |year=2008 |publisher=Breedon Books |location=Derby |isbn=978-1-85983-633-0 |pages=406–207, 420–421 }}</ref><ref name="Players' and fans' pick of the year McGurk proud">{{cite news| title = Players' and fans' pick of the year McGurk proud| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/news/7982320.Players__and_fans__pick_of_the_year_McGurk_proud/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 1 May 2006| accessdate = 4 April 2014| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131156/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/news/7982320.Players__and_fans__pick_of_the_year_McGurk_proud/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Big clubs should do more to help">{{cite news| title = Big clubs should do more to help| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/news/7982262.Big_clubs_should_do_more_to_help/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 29 April 2006| accessdate = 4 April 2014| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131554/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/news/7982262.Big_clubs_should_do_more_to_help/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。季後他與球會續約至2007年<ref name="Clayton’s new City deal">{{Cite news| title = Clayton’s new City deal| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/826456.claytons_new_city_deal/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 11 July 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131557/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/826456.claytons_new_city_deal/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

