約克城教練[[比利·麥克尤恩|比利·麥克尤恩]]在9月時把唐纳德森比作[[保罗·万乔普|保罗·万乔普]]<ref name="‘Donaldinho’ is our Wanchope to watch says McEwan">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = ‘Donaldinho’ is our Wanchope to watch says McEwan| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/925084.donaldinho_is_our_wanchope_to_watch_says_mcewan/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 18 September 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-12-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221010953/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/925084.donaldinho_is_our_wanchope_to_watch_says_mcewan/| dead-url = no}}</ref>，但在10月以2-0敗給[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津联]]後，麥克尤恩批評唐纳德森在進攻上自私使球隊付出代價<ref name="Clayton – Don’t be greedy">{{Cite news| first = Claire| last = Hughes| title = Clayton – Don’t be greedy| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/946937.clayton_dont_be_greedy/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 2 October 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-12-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221011015/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/946937.clayton_dont_be_greedy/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2006年底，唐纳德森成為轉會傳言的主題人物。[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]教練[[米克·麥卡錫|米克·麥卡錫]]在2006年11月觀看了他在1-0擊敗[[奥特林查姆足球俱乐部|奥特林查姆]]的比賽，該比賽唐纳德森打進個人在賽季的第12顆進球<ref name="McEwan stands firm over Donaldson">{{Cite news| title = McEwan stands firm over Donaldson| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6121060.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 6 November 2006| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220421073356/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6121060.stm}}</ref>。此外蘇超球會[[希伯尼安足球俱乐部|希伯尼安]]亦有派人觀看他的比賽表現<ref name="Clayton plays down bid talk">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Clayton plays down bid talk| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1054403.clayton_plays_down_bid_talk/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 2 December 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-12-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221011001/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1054403.clayton_plays_down_bid_talk/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

