2006年12月18日，唐纳德森拒絕了球會提供的一份新合約，意味著他季後便成為自由身<ref name="Donaldson rejects down York deal">{{Cite news| title = Donaldson rejects down York deal| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6190795.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 18 December 2006| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423120814/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6190795.stm}}</ref>。[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯坎索普联]]和[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼得伯勒联]]足球總監在2006年12月觀看了他的比賽<ref name="Donaldson’s touch of class">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Donaldson’s touch of class| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1090740.donaldsons_touch_of_class/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 27 December 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103092138/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1090740.donaldsons_touch_of_class/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Posh push for Donaldson">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Posh push for Donaldson| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1096463.posh_push_for_donaldson/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 30 December 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103092025/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1096463.posh_push_for_donaldson/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。彼得伯勒联出價10萬鎊出購唐纳德森，但出價未能使約克城滿意而告吹<ref name="Posh push for Donaldson"/><ref name="Posh will not up Donaldson offer">{{Cite news| title = Posh will not up Donaldson offer| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6227587.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 3 January 2007| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423082815/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6227587.stm}}</ref>，據報2007年1月約克城替唐纳德森標價50萬鎊<ref name="York put half a million price tag on striker">{{Cite news| title = York put half a million price tag on striker| url = http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=39677| publisher = Non-League Daily| date = 14 January 2007| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214192645/http://www.nonleaguedaily.com/news/index.php?newsmode=FULL&nid=39677| archivedate = 2012年2月14日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>。[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|艾宁顿斯坦利]]提議現金加球員來換取唐纳德森，但艾宁顿斯坦利的25,000鎊的出價被約克城拒絕。後來艾宁顿斯坦利加碼至六位數，但約克城回覆說他是非賣品<ref name="York turn down bid for Donaldson">{{Cite news| title = York turn down bid for Donaldson| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6274291.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 18 January 2007| accessdate = 11 July 2011}}</ref><ref name="Hartlepool midfielder joins York">{{Cite news| title = Hartlepool midfielder joins York| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6279955.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 19 January 2007| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2019-05-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190525162708/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6279955.stm}}</ref><ref name="Stanley £25,000 bid for Clayton ‘derisory’">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Stanley £25,000 bid for Clayton ‘derisory’| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1133815.stanley_25_000_bid_for_clayton_derisory/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 19 January 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131409/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1133815.stanley_25_000_bid_for_clayton_derisory/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2007年1月20日以2-1不敵[[京达米士特足球俱乐部|京达米士特]]的賽事，唐纳德森因為用手肘而吃紅牌及停賽3場<ref name="Billy steps up search after Clayton sees red">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Billy steps up search after Clayton sees red| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1138287.billy_steps_up_search_after_clayton_sees_red/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 22 January 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-01-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180108174752/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1138287.billy_steps_up_search_after_clayton_sees_red/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。之後斯坎索普出價買入唐纳德森，但約克城認為未符合他的身價而拒絕<ref name="City reject new Clayton bid">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = City reject new Clayton bid| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1142259.city_reject_new_clayton_bid/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 24 January 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-02-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180207005620/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1142259.City_reject_new_Clayton_bid/| dead-url = no}}</ref>，之後斯坎索普教練稱他不會花大錢簽下唐纳德森<ref name="Iron unlikely to up Clayton offer">{{Cite news| title = Iron unlikely to up Clayton offer| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1145698.iron_unlikely_to_up_clayton_offer/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 25 January 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-02-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180207010400/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1145698.Iron_unlikely_to_up_Clayton_offer/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2007年1月29日，希伯尼安宣佈已與唐纳德森簽下三年合約<ref>{{cite news |first=Steve |last=Carroll |title=Hibs net a 'gem' in Clayton |url=http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1155630.hibs_net_a_gem_in_clayton/ |newspaper=The Press |location=York |date=30 January 2007 |accessdate=14 July 2010 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108063708/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1155630.hibs_net_a_gem_in_clayton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。希伯尼安希望立即唐纳德森帶到蘇格蘭並出價5萬鎊立即收購，但被約克城拒絕<ref name="York angry at Donaldson transfer">{{Cite news| title = York angry at Donaldson transfer| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6314169.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 30 January 2007| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423120816/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6314169.stm}}</ref>，約克城教練希望他能完成其合約才離隊<ref name="Carry on Clayton - McEwan">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Carry on Clayton – McEwan| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1159006.carry_on_clayton_mcewan/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 30 January 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-01-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180108063834/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1159006.carry_on_clayton_mcewan/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2007年2月6日，唐纳德森停賽完畢並代表球會出戰對奥特林查姆的比賽<ref>{{cite news |first=Dave |last=Flett |title=Look who's back – it's Clayton |url=http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1181630.look_whos_back_its_clayton/ |newspaper=The Press |location=York |date=9 February 2007 |accessdate=14 July 2010 |archive-date=2016-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217194313/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1181630.look_whos_back_its_clayton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，復出後首顆進球是在2007年3月13日對劍橋聯的比賽，演出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref name="McEwan salutes hat-trick ace Donaldson">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = McEwan salutes hat-trick ace Donaldson| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1258088.mcewan_salutes_hattrick_ace_donaldson/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 14 March 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-12-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161217194402/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1258088.mcewan_salutes_hattrick_ace_donaldson/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。4月，有關他無心留戀約克城的傳言四散，唐纳德森表示他會全力以赴代表約克城出戰餘下賽事<ref>{{Cite news |first=Dave |last=Flett |title=Ascent into league fires City's 'Donaldo' |url=http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1352951.ascent_into_league_fires_citys_donaldo/ |newspaper=The Press |location=York |date=25 April 2007 |accessdate=4 July 2010 |archive-date=2016-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217194423/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1352951.ascent_into_league_fires_citys_donaldo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006/07球季他共替約克城打進26球<ref name="The Complete Record 2006-07">{{cite book |last=Batters |title=York City: The Complete Record |pages=408–409, 420–421}}</ref>，其中24球是聯賽進球，使他在射手榜排行第三<ref name="Rothmans2007-08">{{cite book| editor1-first = Glenda| editor1-last = Rollin| editor2-first = Jack| editor2-last = Rollin| title = Sky Sports Football Yearbook 2007–2008| year = 2007| publisher = Headline Publishing Group| location = London| isbn = 978-0-7553-1664-9| page = 627 }}</ref>。

===希伯尼安===
唐纳德森在2007年7月10日的季前熱身賽對[[布里金城足球會|布里金城]]打進在希伯尼安的首顆進球<ref name="Reports: Brechin 0 Hibernian 2">{{cite web| title = Reports: Brechin 0 Hibernian 2| url = http://www.hibs.co.uk/news/more.php?id=2263_0_1_0_C| publisher = Hibernian F.C| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070901215010/http://www.hibs.co.uk/news/more.php?id=2263_0_1_0_C| archivedate = 2007年9月1日| deadurl = yes| accessdate = 2016年4月28日}}</ref>。2007年8月，他在[[蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽_(1998年-2013年)|蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽]]首場比賽便是對宿敵[[哈茨足球俱乐部|哈茨]]，9月透過主射[[點球|點球]]打進在希伯尼安首顆聯賽進球，擊敗[[法尔科克足球俱乐部|法尔科克]]<ref name="Hearts 0-1 Hibernian">{{Cite news| first = Clive| last = Lindsay| title = Hearts 0–1 Hibernian| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/6928896.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 6 August 2007| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423102222/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/6928896.stm}}</ref><ref name="Falkirk 1-1 Hibernian">{{Cite news| title = Falkirk 1–1 Hibernian| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/6988282.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 15 September 2007| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220417223900/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/6988282.stm}}</ref>，可是他在這比賽中吃紅牌離場<ref name="Collins left to rue sending off">{{Cite news| title = Collins left to rue sending off| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6996664.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 15 September 2007| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423193458/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6996664.stm}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Clay just desperate to hear Hibees roar |url=http://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/competitions/premiership/clay-just-desperate-to-hear-hibees-roar-1-1333118 |newspaper=The Scotsman |location=Edinburgh |date=26 September 2007 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2017-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213091346/https://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/competitions/premiership/clay-just-desperate-to-hear-hibees-roar-1-1333118 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。停賽完畢後首場比賽是[[蘇格蘭聯賽盃|蘇格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|马瑟韦尔]]並攻入一球<ref name="Hibernian 2-4 Motherwell">{{Cite news| title = Hibernian 2–4 Motherwell| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_cups/7011022.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 26 September 2007| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220417225557/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_cups/7011022.stm}}</ref>。之後唐纳德森在聯賽對[[基马诺克足球俱乐部|基马诺克]]的比賽戴帽<ref name="Hibernian 4-1 Kilmarnock">{{Cite news| title = Hibernian 4–1 Kilmarnock| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/7017189.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 29 September 2007| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220425183218/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/7017189.stm}}</ref>。

唐纳德森未在新教練[[米克苏·帕特莱宁|米克苏·帕特莱宁]]的計劃中，在2008年2月傳出[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克鲁]]有意簽下他<ref name="Clayton’s Crewe’s control">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Clayton’s Crewe’s control| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/2076294.claytons_crewes_control/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 27 February 2008| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131600/https://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/2076294.claytons_crewes_control/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Clayton Donaldson Keen To Grab First Team Chance Again">{{Cite news| title = Clayton Donaldson Keen To Grab First Team Chance Again| url = http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/clayton-donaldson-keen-to-grab-first-970795| newspaper = Daily Record| location = Glasgow| date = 7 March 2008| accessdate = 17 September 2012| archive-date = 2019-04-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190415220323/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/clayton-donaldson-keen-to-grab-first-970795| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2007/08賽季他在各項賽事上場21次打進6球，最後進球是2007年12月對法尔科克的比賽。季後傳出[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|达灵顿]]有意簽下唐纳德森<ref name="Quakers target striker Donaldson">{{Cite news| title = Quakers target striker Donaldson| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7463773.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 19 June 2008| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423102223/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7463773.stm}}</ref>，最終會方告訴唐纳德森他被掛牌求售<ref name="Paatelainen orders up to nine players to move on">{{Cite news| title = Paatelainen orders up to nine players to move on| url = http://www.scotsman.com/sport/paatelainen_orders_up_to_nine_players_to_move_on_1_1083159| newspaper = The Scotsman| location = Edinburgh| date = 1 August 2008| accessdate = 9 November 2011| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103091932/https://www.scotsman.com/sport/paatelainen_orders_up_to_nine_players_to_move_on_1_1083159| dead-url = no}}</ref>。克魯在賣掉射手[[尼基·梅纳德|尼基·梅纳德]]獲得225萬鎊資金後，傳出會收資簽下他並已與唐纳德森展開談判<ref name="Pinau arrives at Easter Road">{{Cite news| title = Pinau arrives at Easter Road| url = http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/12390389.Pinau_arrives_at_Easter_Road/| newspaper = The Herald| location = Glasgow| date = 13 August 2008| accessdate = 10 November 2015| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103091956/https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/12390389.Pinau_arrives_at_Easter_Road/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Life after Nicky">{{Cite news| first = Toby| last = Robinson| title = Life after Nicky| url = http://www.creweguardian.co.uk/sport/3576589.Life_after_Nicky/| newspaper = Crewe & Nantwich Guardian| date = 7 August 2008| accessdate = 4 April 2014| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103131407/https://www.creweguardian.co.uk/sport/3576589.Life_after_Nicky/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。雙方球會最終同意一筆六位數的轉會費，唐纳德森亦同意合約條款，轉會至克魯<ref name="Crewe Alex: Six-figure deal for Donaldson">{{Cite news| title = Crewe Alex: Six-figure deal for Donaldson| url = http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/Crewe-Alex-figure-deal-Donaldson/story-12552192-detail/story.html| newspaper = The Sentinel| location = Stoke-on-Trent| date = 15 August 2008| accessdate = 5 April 2014| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161217214220/http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/crewe-alex-figure-deal-donaldson/story-12552192-detail/story.html| archivedate = 2016年12月17日}}</ref><ref name="Donaldson set to leave Hibs for Crewe">{{Cite news| title = Donaldson set to leave Hibs for Crewe| url = http://www.scotsman.com/sport/donaldson_set_to_leave_hibs_for_crewe_1_1269400| newspaper = The Scotsman| location = Edinburgh| date = 15 August 2008| accessdate = 9 November 2011| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103170453/https://www.scotsman.com/sport/donaldson_set_to_leave_hibs_for_crewe_1_1269400| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

===克魯===
2008年8月18日，唐纳德森轉會至克魯並簽約三年<ref name="Crewe add Donaldson to forwards">{{Cite news| title = Crewe add Donaldson to forwards| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7541447.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 18 August 2008| accessdate = 11 July 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423193502/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7541447.stm}}</ref>。8月23日，他首次代表球會上場參與2-1擊敗[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|沃尔索尔]]的比賽，在81分鐘替補換入<ref name="Crewe 2–1 Walsall">{{Cite news| title = Crewe 2–1 Walsall| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7565026.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 23 August 2008| accessdate = 2 April 2011}}</ref>。11月，他在對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]的賽事打進在克魯的首顆進球，最終仍以3-2戰敗收場<ref name="Huddersfield 3-2 Crewe">{{Cite news| title = Huddersfield 3–2 Crewe| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7686088.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 1 November 2008| accessdate = 1 November 2008| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423082815/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7686088.stm}}</ref>。接著的足總盃第一輪他打進致勝球，以1-0擊敗[[艾贝斯费特联足球俱乐部|艾贝斯费特联]]晉級<ref name="Crewe 1-0 Ebbsfleet">{{Cite news| title = Crewe 1–0 Ebbsfleet| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7700351.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 8 November 2008| accessdate = 8 November 2008}}</ref>。2008/09球季，他在各項賽事上場43次共打進7球。

2009年8月，他因腓骨斷裂而傷出8週<ref name="Button back with Crewe">{{Cite news| title = Button back with Crewe| url = http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11675/5530648/button-back-with-crewe| publisher = Sky Sports| date = 1 September 2009| accessdate = 30 June 2014| archive-date = 2017-12-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171213010927/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11675/5530648/button-back-with-crewe| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2009/10球季，唐纳德森在各項賽事上場39次共打進13球。2010/11賽季首次上場是8月7日對靴尔福特联<ref>{{cite news |title=Crewe 0–1 Hereford |url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8842786.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=7 August 2010 |accessdate=2 April 2011 |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524203441/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8842786.stm }}</ref>，8月21日7-0大勝[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|巴尼特]]的比賽打進在新球季的首顆進球<ref>{{cite news |title=Crewe 7–0 Barnet |url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/8913059.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=21 August 2010 |accessdate=21 August 2010}}</ref>。該球季他上場48次打進29球，其中28球是聯賽進球，使他成為當季英乙神射手<ref>{{cite book |editor1-first=Glenda |editor1-last=Rollin |editor2-first=Jack |editor2-last=Rollin |title=Sky Sports Football Yearbook 2011–2012 |year=2011 |publisher=Headline Publishing Group |location=London |isbn=978-0-7553-6231-8 |page=42}}</ref>。

===布伦特福德===
[[File:Clayton_Donaldson_18-04-2014_1.jpg|thumb]]的唐纳德森]]

唐纳德森在2011年7月1日以自由身與英甲球會[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|布伦特福德]]簽下三年合約<ref>{{cite news |title=Brentford sign striker Clayton Donaldson from Crewe |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/13997756 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 July 2011 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405074214/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/13997756 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Crewe Alex: Donaldson confirms Crewe exit by joining Bees">{{Cite news| title = Crewe Alex: Donaldson confirms Crewe exit by joining Bees| url = http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/Crewe-Alex-Donaldson-confirms-Crewe-exit-joining/story-12868126-detail/story.html| newspaper = The Sentinel| location = Stoke-on-Trent| date = 2 July 2011| accessdate = 4 April 2014| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140405104550/http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/Crewe-Alex-Donaldson-confirms-Crewe-exit-joining/story-12868126-detail/story.html| archivedate = 2014年4月5日}}</ref>。2012/13球季，他當選為布伦特福德年度最佳球員<ref name="Last chance to vote for the Brentford FC Player of the Year 2014/15">{{cite news| first = Chris| last = Wickham| title = Last chance to vote for the Brentford FC Player of the Year 2014/15| url = http://www.brentfordfc.co.uk/news/article/brentford-fc-player-of-the-year-201415-vote-2413665.aspx| publisher = Brentford F.C| date = 29 April 2015| accessdate = 26 May 2015| archive-date = 2016-05-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529143732/http://www.brentfordfc.co.uk/news/article/brentford-fc-player-of-the-year-201415-vote-2413665.aspx| dead-url = no}}</ref>，該季他在各項賽事上場56次打進24球。2013/14球季助球隊取得聯賽亞軍，取得來季在英冠參賽資格後<ref name="C. Donaldson"/>，主教練[[馬克·沃伯頓|馬克·沃伯頓]]確認會向唐纳德森提供一份新合約<ref>{{cite news |title=Clayton Donaldson: Brentford to offer striker new contract |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27593624 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=27 May 2014 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2019-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404150207/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27593624 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
[[File:Clayton_Donaldson_01-08-2015_1.jpg|thumb]]的唐纳德森]]

唐纳德森拒絕了布伦特福德開出的合約，選擇與英冠球會伯明翰簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27928898 |title=Clayton Donaldson: Birmingham City sign Brentford striker |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 June 2014 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411035856/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27928898 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首場比賽是球季揭幕日對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]的比賽，聯賽盃對劍橋聯的賽事打進在伯明翰首球，打開該比場的記錄並以3-1取勝。縱使他的表現得到讚賞<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/lee-clark-backs-birmingham-city-7840888 |title=Lee Clark backs Birmingham City striker Clayton Donaldson to add more goals to his game |first=Colin |last=Tattum |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=26 September 2014 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901153350/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/lee-clark-backs-birmingham-city-7840888 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他本人對進球量偏低感到失望，10月結束前他只再打進1球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-clayton-donaldson-confident-7835042 |title=Birmingham City: Clayton Donaldson confident the goals will come |first=Colin |last=Tattum |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=26 September 2014 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901155358/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-clayton-donaldson-confident-7835042 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教練團和陣形的變動使唐纳德森進球量有所提升，新教練[[加利·路维特|加利·路维特]]偏向把唐纳德森出任單箭頭。對[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]一戰他梅開二度以2-1取勝，延續球季不敗走勢至9場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-clayton-donaldson-reveals-8064685 |title=Birmingham City: Clayton Donaldson reveals how Gary Rowett has banished Blues' doom and gloom |first=Colin |last=Tattum |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=7 November 2014 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901155542/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-clayton-donaldson-reveals-8064685 |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-2-watford-1-8050988 |title=Birmingham City 2 Watford 1 |first=Colin |last=Tattum |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=1 November 2014 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901153817/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-2-watford-1-8050988 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後到訪[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|罗瑟勒姆]]打進全場唯一入球取勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/football/rotherham-united/rotherham-united-0-birmingham-city-1-match-verdict-boss-steve-evans-blasts-disgusting-millers-1-6967933 |title=Rotherham United 0 Birmingham City 1 match verdict: Boss Steve Evans blasts "disgusting" Millers |first=Paul |last=Davis |newspaper=The Star |location=Sheffield |date=24 November 2014 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321175217/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/football/rotherham-united/rotherham-united-0-birmingham-city-1-match-verdict-boss-steve-evans-blasts-disgusting-millers-1-6967933 |archive-date=2016-03-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。3-1擊敗[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]和3-0戰勝[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|威根竞技]]的比賽，唐纳德森共打進了5球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/gary-rowett-birmingham-city-players-8352023 |title=Gary Rowett: My Birmingham City players deserve credit for 'manning up' against Nottingham Forest |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=28 December 2014 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901154058/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/gary-rowett-birmingham-city-players-8352023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中對威根的比賽威戴帽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-can-clayton-donaldson-8423842 |title=Birmingham City: Can Clayton Donaldson become the first Blues player in two decades to score 20 league goals in a season? |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=12 January 2015 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901195906/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-can-clayton-donaldson-8423842 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該球季他在各項賽事打進16球，其中聯賽為15球，並當選為球員選出年度最佳球員及球迷選出年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/players-awards-2015-2438100.aspx |title=Donaldson completes hat-trick at the Players Awards 2015 |first=Jack |last=Burrell |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=3 May 2015 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308102446/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/players-awards-2015-2438100.aspx |archive-date=2016-03-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2015/16球季首個月份，唐纳德森交出4助交但沒有進球。9月12日對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]，他在上半場就完成帽子戲法，以4-2全取3分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/clayton-donaldson-birmingham-city-jon-toral-2685298.aspx |title=Clayton Donaldson on his hat-trick |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=13 September 2015 |accessdate=16 September 2015 |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413061214/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/clayton-donaldson-birmingham-city-jon-toral-2685298.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球季聯賽第5顆進球是11月7日對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富勒姆]]的賽事<ref name=sb1516/，之後他赴牙買加代表國家隊參賽。之後他帶[[鼠蹊部|鼠蹊傷]]回到球會並需休養6星期。教練路维特說如果他沒有在國際賽踢畢整場比賽，傷勢會比較輕，但牙買加教練[[雲費特·舒哈化|雲費特·舒哈化]]否認指控，指他欲換下唐纳德森但球員本人希望踢整場比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/34900916 |title=Birmingham City: Striker search stepped up after Donaldson blow |publisher=BBC Sport |date=24 November 2015 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903092043/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/34900916 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sportsmax.tv/?q=articles/2015/11/24/jamaica-football-i-have-never-played-injured-player-schaefer-taken-aback |title=Jamaica Football: 'I have never played an injured player' Schaefer taken aback by Birmingham accusations |publisher=Digicel SportsMax |date=24 November 2015 |accessdate=29 December 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305050105/http://www.sportsmax.tv/?q=articles%2F2015%2F11%2F24%2Fjamaica-football-i-have-never-played-injured-player-schaefer-taken-aback |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月26日，唐纳德森回歸球場，對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]的比賽在3-0落後時替補換入<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35139004 |title=Sheff Wed 3–0 Birmingham |publisher=BBC Sport |date=26 December 2015 |accessdate=21 March 2016 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728085008/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35139004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
唐纳德森曾入選[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格兰全国联赛选手队]]，代表英格蘭非聯賽層級參加歐洲挑戰盃對比利時一戰<ref name="Morecambe provide England quartet">{{cite web| title = Morecambe provide England quartet| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/4349160.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 17 October 2005| accessdate = 2 April 2011| archive-date = 2022-04-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423193503/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/4349160.stm}}</ref>，此外他還入選2006年5月四國邀請賽的35人初選名單<ref name="Fairclough names 35-man squad">{{cite web| title = Fairclough names 35-man squad| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/4964526.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2 May 2006| accessdate = 2 April 2011}}</ref>，最後更入選22人最後名單<ref name="National call-up for Clayton">{{Cite news| title = National call-up for Clayton| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1017320.national_callup_for_clayton/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 11 November 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-03-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010909/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1017320.national_callup_for_clayton/| dead-url = no}}</ref>和上場陣容的16人名單，出戰2006年11月對荷蘭的賽事<ref name="Clayton makes the cut">{{Cite news| title = Clayton makes the cut| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1032432.clayton_makes_the_cut/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 21 November 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-08-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180829152226/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1032432.Clayton_makes_the_cut/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。唐纳德森在比賽結束前15分鐘入替上場，交出一助攻使英格蘭以4-1取勝<ref name="Billy lets rip at international snub">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Billy lets rip at international snub| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1053060.billy_lets_rip_at_international_snub/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 1 December 2006| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2016-12-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221010950/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1053060.billy_lets_rip_at_international_snub/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

唐纳德森入選2007年2月對北愛爾蘭的大軍名軍<ref name="Donaldson makes England XI squad">{{cite news| title = Donaldson makes England XI squad| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/6311231.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 31 January 2007| accessdate = 31 January 2007}}</ref>，但約克城教練欲把他從大軍名單除下<ref name="Billy hails strength in depth as Minstermen revel in top-notch win">{{Cite news| first = Dave| last = Flett| title = Billy hails strength in depth as Minstermen revel in top-notch win| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1186554.billy_hails_strength_in_depth_as_minstermen_revel_in_topnotch_win/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 12 February 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-08-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180829152230/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1186554.billy_hails_strength_in_depth_as_minstermen_revel_in_topnotch_win/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。最終唐纳德森在該比賽中先發上場，但在50分鐘被換下，最終英格蘭以3-1戰敗<ref name="Donaldson takes first 50">{{Cite news| title = Donaldson takes first 50| url = http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1190972.donaldson_takes_first_50/| newspaper = The Press| location = York| date = 14 February 2007| accessdate = 14 July 2010| archive-date = 2018-08-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180829105954/http://www.yorkpress.co.uk/sport/1190972.Donaldson_takes_first_50/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年4月，唐纳德森宣佈他會代表父母的祖國[[牙買加國家足球隊|牙買加]]出賽。他希望能參加[[2015年美洲盃足球賽|2015年美洲盃足球賽]]或[[2015年美洲金盃|2015年美洲金盃]]，但因未能趕及得到牙買加護照而落空<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.digicelsportsmax.com/?q=articles/2015/04/22/jamaica-football-clayton-hopes-hard-work-leads-national-call |title=Jamaica Football: Clayton hopes hard work leads to national call-up |publisher=Digicel-SportsMax |date=22 April 2015 |accessdate=28 April 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074724/http://www.digicelsportsmax.com/?q=articles%2F2015%2F04%2F22%2Fjamaica-football-clayton-hopes-hard-work-leads-national-call |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-star-clayton-donaldson-10439352 |title=Birmingham City star Clayton Donaldson insists Jamaica commitments won't affect Blues |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=13 November 2015 |accessdate=14 November 2015 |archive-date=2018-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723064155/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-star-clayton-donaldson-10439352 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月，他被牙買加徵召參加[[2018年世界盃外圍賽|2018年世界盃外圍賽]]對[[巴拿馬國家足球隊|巴拿馬]]和[[海地國家足球隊|海地]]的賽事並在該兩場賽事上場，在11月13日在[[京斯敦|京斯敦]]完成國家隊首秀，在2-0落後巴拿馬時以替補身份上場，但未能助球隊取得進球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/article/sports/20151113/reggae-boyz-lose-2-0-against-panama-semi-final-round-opener |title=Reggae Boyz lose 2–0 against Panama in semi-final round opener |first=Audley |last=Boyd |newspaper=Jamaica Gleaner |date=13 November 2015 |accessdate=14 November 2015 |archive-date=2018-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723004126/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/article/sports/20151113/reggae-boyz-lose-2-0-against-panama-semi-final-round-opener |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=2000062536/match=300334125/ |title=2018 FIFA World Cup Russia: North, Central America and Caribbean matches: Jamaica 0–2 Panama |publisher=FIFA |date=13 November 2015 |accessdate=14 November 2015 |archive-date=2018-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723003935/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=2000062536/match=300334125/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對海地的比賽，他先發出場並在62分鐘打進全場唯一進球，接應開出的角球以頭槌頂進<ref name="Jamaica edges Haiti on Donaldson">{{cite web |url=http://www.concacaf.com/article/jamaica-edges-haiti-on-donaldson-goal |title=Jamaica edges Haiti on Donaldson goal |publisher=CONCACAF |date=17 November 2015 |accessdate=28 February 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121105901/http://www.concacaf.com/article/jamaica-edges-haiti-on-donaldson-goal |archivedate=2015年11月21日 }}</ref>。

